OL,3,CFire service in Hawick cutback in cost
OL,4,Csaving exercise
OL,6,FThe Scottish Fire and Rescue Service
OL,7,FBoard has today (June 22) made the
OL,8,Fdecision to scale-back on the
OL,9,Fpermanently based fire service in
OL,10,FHawick.
OL,12,FIt's part of a number of of
OL,13,Frecommendations on proposed changes to
OL,14,Fmore than 30 fire stations across
OL,15,FScotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782150513
OL,3,CFire service in Hawick cutback in cost
OL,4,Csaving exercise
OL,6,FWhen the proposals were first
OL,7,Fannounced in May 2025, a campaign was
OL,8,Fstarted to keep the staffing as it
OL,9,Fwas, with campaigners concerned that
OL,10,Fan on-call system would result in
OL,11,Flonger call-out response times which
OL,12,Fcould potentially prove fatal.
OL,14,FThe Scottish Fire and Rescue service
OL,15,FBoard members in the meeting reported
OL,16,FHawick had the second lowest demand in
OL,17,FScotland compared to stations with
OL,18,Fsimilar staffing.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782150513
OL,3,CFire service in Hawick cutback in cost
OL,4,Csaving exercise
OL,6,F"People in Hawick and the surrounding
OL,7,Fareas will feel very badly let down
OL,8,Fand feel betrayed," Cllr Stuart
OL,9,FMarshall believes.
OL,11,F"There's been a campaign in this area
OL,12,Fto save this fire station from being
OL,13,Fscaled down and here we go again,
OL,14,Fanother major frontline service is
OL,15,Fbeing stripped back and it's
OL,16,Fabsolutely appalling."
OL,18,FMSP, Rachael Hamilton said: "The
OL,19,Fcommunity will undoubtedly be
OL,20,Fdisappointed if Hawick Fire Station is
OL,21,Fdowngraded.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782150513
OL,3,CFire service in Hawick cutback in cost
OL,4,Csaving exercise
OL,6,F"It provides an incredible service
OL,7,Fthat that reaches way across the
OL,8,Fgeographical spread of the borders,
OL,9,Fbecause it is in a rural location. I
OL,10,Fthink the community will drive a
OL,11,Fcampaign an appeal against this. I
OL,12,Fwill be 100% behind them."
OL,14,FChanges agreed today impacting the
OL,15,FBorders will see the introduction of a
OL,16,FDay Shift Duty System crewing for the
OL,17,Fprimary fire engine at Hawick, which
OL,18,Fis currently crewed by firefighters
OL,19,Fpermanently based at the station.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782150513
OL,3,CFire service in Hawick cutback in cost
OL,4,Csaving exercise
OL,6,FThis will mean that crews would only
OL,7,Fbe there during the day from Monday to
OL,8,FFriday, with on call firefighters
OL,9,Finstead covering weekends and
OL,10,Fovernights.
OL,12,FThe second fire engine will remain
OL,13,Fcrewed by on-call firefighters.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782150513
OL,3,CFire service in Hawick cutback in cost
OL,4,Csaving exercise
OL,6,FThe fire service explained that
OL,7,FHawick's roof structure is affected by
OL,8,FReinforced Autoclaved Aerated Concrete
OL,9,F(RAAC) and that urgent repairs are
OL,10,Frequired. But they are unable to begin
OL,11,Frepair work until a decision is made
OL,12,Fon the station configuration and duty
OL,13,Fsystem.
OL,15,FIn Galashiels there's an amendment for
OL,16,Fthe Nucleus Crew where further
OL,17,Fpermanent employees would be in place
OL,18,Fto support on call availability during
OL,19,Fday shift hours.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782150513
OL,3,CFire service in Hawick cutback in cost
OL,4,Csaving exercise
OL,6,FThey say the station there is in a
OL,7,Fprime location to support on call
OL,8,Favailability across the area.
OL,10,FAn announcement from the Scottish Fire
OL,11,Fand Rescue Service Board is expected
OL,12,Flater this week with more details of
OL,13,Fwhat this will mean for the station in
OL,14,FHawick.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/7
